description:
*Effective 7-1-93 (per barrel). "Barrel" means 42 U.S. Gallons of Petroleum Products.				
***Other fuel includes Ethanol, Methanol, Biodiesel, Naphtha, Compressed Natural Gas, and Liquefied Natural Gas.
